  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Experience the rush of aerial combat as you engage in history's most iconic airborne missions. Annihilate your enemies as you launch into massive dogfights and aerial bombing missions. Battle for supremacy over stunning landscapes from the patchwork fields of Southern England to the smoking ruins of Stalingrad. * Battle hundreds of enemy aces for control of the skies in intense multiplayer dogfights and bombing sorties * Choose a difficulty level to match your experience from adrenaline-fueled arcade action to realistic simulations * Relive the golden age of military aviation piloting 13 classic aircraft through 42 death-defying missions.",
